    .desc = A rooty tooty point and shooty.

ent-WeaponRevolverDeckard = NT Deckard (.45 magnum)
    .desc = A rare, civilian grade custom-built revolver. Use when there is no time for Voight-Kampff test. Uses .45 magnum ammo.

